sequenceDiagram
    participant Staff
    participant API
    participant DB
    participant ImageGen as GatePassService
    participant WA as WhatsApp
    participant Visitor
    participant Security

    Staff->>API: Approve Visit
    API->>DB: Generate Check-In OTP (8hr expiry)
    API->>ImageGen: Request Gate Pass Image
    ImageGen->>ImageGen: Fetch Photo (GCP) + Overlay OTP
    ImageGen-->>API: Return Image Buffer
    API->>DB: Save Image (Base64)
    API->>WA: Send Gate Pass Image
    WA-->>Visitor: Receive Image on WhatsApp
    
    Note over Visitor, Security: Physical Arrival
    
    Visitor->>Security: Show Gate Pass (OTP)
    Security->>API: POST /visitors/verify-checkin-otp
    API-->>Security: Valid (Show details)
    Security->>API: POST /checkin/:visitId
    API->>DB: Mark Visit Active
